          <p class="text-hover" data-img="five">I have come into contact with <strong>blockchain technology</strong> while learning coding. Afterwards I have significantly deepened my knowledge during supporting the Earlybird Investment team in the area of blockchain and fintech. After writing my bachelor thesis about the intersection between blockchain and <strong>venture capital</strong> I have started working for Signature Ventures. I considerably contributed to building up this venture fund from scratch.</p>
